ing women athletes like Yousofi to flee the country to escape prosecution.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.99372386450305, \"rank\": 0.006176369340303644, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women's access\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"parks\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"gyms\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"women athletes\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"Yousofi\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecution\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheInternational Olympic Committeeannounced last month a gender-equal team of six athletes would represent Afghanistan in Paris but no Taliban official would be allowed.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.882995356599529, \"rank\": 0.1325086966873741, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999971561664516, \"rank\": 2.843841557295897e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.99372386450305, \"rank\": 0.006176369340303644, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc