ics\", \"score\": 0.9998715915242473, \"rank\": 0.0001273182565766654, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yousofi\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"her third appearance\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an honour to represent the girls of my homeland once again,\\\" Yousofi said in an AOC statement on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999989506475946, \"rank\": 1.0493623330456135e-05, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an honour\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"my homeland\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"Yousofi\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Girls and women who have been deprived of basic rights, including education, which is the most important one.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Girls\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"basic rights\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I represent the stolen dreams and aspirations of these women.\\\"\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stolen dreams\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"aspirations\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"these women\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked for comment, Atal Mushwanay, spokesman for the Taliban government's sports directorate, said: \\\"We have no opinion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Youcef_Atal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atal\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Youcef_Atal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Youcef_Atal\"}, {\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.99372386450305, \"rank\": 0.006176369340303644, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comment\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"spokesman\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"no opinion\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yousofi, 28, thanked the AOC and also expressed her gratitude to Afghanistan's Olympic committee, whose top officials are in exile, for \\\"giving us the chance to relive and pursue our dreams\\\".\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999989506475946, \"rank\": 1.0493623330456135e-05, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.882995356599529, \"rank\": 0.1325086966873741, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \