2995356599529, \"rank\": 0.1325086966873741, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her story\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"basic rights\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yousofi's coach John Quinn will be the Afghanistan team's head coach in Paris.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_R._Quinn\", \"score\": 0.9998514556789739, \"rank\": 8.33659521010467e-05, \"text\": \"John Quinn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_R._Quinn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_R._Quinn\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.882995356599529, \"rank\": 0.1325086966873741, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999971561664516, \"rank\": 2.843841557295897e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yousofi's coach\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the track she has improved enormously technically since coming here and she has a great squad around her,\\\" Quinn said.\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quinn_Fabray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.8055822681958762e-12, \"text\": \"Quinn\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quinn_Fabray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quinn_Fabray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"a great squad\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when you consider everything else she has had to juggle \\u00c3\\u00a2\\u00c2\\u20ac\\u00c2\\\" training, a new language, getting her family here, all those things, she has been amazing.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c3\\u00a2\\u00c2\\u20ac\\u00c2\\\" training\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"a new language\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her efforts have certainly inspired the other squad members.\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her efforts\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"the other squad members\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now she finds herself on the world stage again in Paris,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2837, \"end\": 2842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999971561664516, \"rank\": 2.843841557295897e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independe